---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="astro-agent-annotate — annotate the UI, paste to your agent">
  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      const KEY_PREFIX = "aaa:annotations:";
      const SEED_FLAG = "aaa:demo-seeded-v1";
      try {
        if (localStorage.getItem(SEED_FLAG)) return;
        for (let i = 0; i < localStorage.length; i++) {
          const k = localStorage.key(i);
          if (k && k.startsWith(KEY_PREFIX)) {
            localStorage.setItem(SEED_FLAG, "1");
            return;
          }
        }
        const now = Date.now();
        const uuid = () =>
          (crypto && crypto.randomUUID && crypto.randomUUID()) ||
          Math.random().toString(36).slice(2);
        const annotations = [
          {
            id: uuid(),
            note: "Stronger contrast — this eyebrow nearly disappears on the gradient.",
            source: "src/pages/index.astro:11:5",
            selector: "main > section.hero > span.eyebrow",
            tag: "span",
            html: '<span class="eyebrow">Astro dev toolbar plugin</span>',
            createdAt: now - 60000,
          },
          {
            id: uuid(),
            note: 'Rename to "Hold Alt + click" — "point and click" is ambiguous.',
            source: "src/pages/index.astro:30:11",
            selector: "main > ol.steps > li:nth-of-type(1) > h3",
            tag: "h3",
            html: "<h3>Point and click</h3>",
            createdAt: now - 30000,
          },
        ];
        localStorage.setItem(KEY_PREFIX + "/", JSON.stringify(annotations));
        localStorage.setItem(SEED_FLAG, "1");
      } catch (_) {
        /* ignore — localStorage unavailable */
      }
    })();
  </script>

  <section class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Astro dev toolbar plugin</span>
    <h1>Annotate any UI element.<br/>Paste it all into your agent.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      You're building a site with Claude or Cursor. You see five things to change. Instead of
      describing each one in words — <em>"the second card, the one with the gradient, has the wrong padding on mobile"</em> — you Alt+click each, type a short note, then copy them all to your clipboard.
    </p>
    <div class="cta">
      <span class="key">Hold <kbd>Alt</kbd></span>
      <span class="plus">+</span>
      <span class="key">Click any element on this page</span>
    </div>
    <p class="hint">…or click the tag icon in the Astro dev toolbar below.</p>
  </section>

  <figure class="demo">
    <img src="/demo.gif" alt="Annotating elements and copying notes to the clipboard" />
  </figure>

  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <ol class="steps">
    <li>
      <h3>Point and click</h3>
      <p>Hold Alt to highlight the element under your cursor. Click to attach a note.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Keep working</h3>
      <p>Each annotated element gets a small purple bubble. They persist across reloads and follow you across routes.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Copy to the agent</h3>
      <p>Open the toolbar, click <strong>Copy</strong>. You get a clean markdown block grouped by page, with source paths like <code>src/components/Hero.astro:7:23</code>.</p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h2>What gets copied</h2>
  <p>Markdown, grouped by page. No XML, no JSON. Paste it straight into the chat:</p>
  <div class="chat">
    <div class="avatar" aria-hidden="true">Y</div>
    <div class="bubble">
      <div class="bubble-meta">You · pasted from the dev toolbar</div>
      <pre><code># Annotations
_Collected 2026-05-22T19:00:00.000Z_

## `/` — 2 notes

1. **CTA is hard to find on mobile**
   - `src/components/Hero.astro:7:23`
   - `&lt;button class="cta"&gt;Get started&lt;/button&gt;`
2. **Cards should be 3-column on desktop**
   - `src/pages/index.astro:18:5`</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Try this page</h2>
  <p>
    Two annotations are already seeded — see the purple bubbles? Hover Alt to add more. Spot a wording you'd change, a button style that bugs you, a heading you'd reword. Click it, type whatever you'd say to the agent.
  </p>

  <div class="cards">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Built for vibe-coders</h3>
      <p>Less time typing context, more time shipping. The agent gets the exact file, line, and your intent.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Cross-page sessions</h3>
      <p>Annotate the homepage, navigate to <a href="/walkthrough" class="link">/walkthrough</a>, annotate more. The toolbar collects every note from every route until you copy.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Dev-only</h3>
      <p>Vite plugin and toolbar app only register during <code>astro dev</code>. Your production bundle is untouched.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Astro-native</h3>
      <p>Lives in the Astro dev toolbar where you already are. No extension, no Chrome integration.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <style>
    .hero { padding-top: 8px; }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(56px, 7.5vw, 88px);
      line-height: 0.96;
      max-width: 11ch;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    figure.demo {
      margin: 32px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--panel);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }
    figure.demo img { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; }

    .chat {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin: 12px 0 18px;
    }
    .chat .avatar {
      flex: none;
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #ffffff;
      font: 700 13px/34px ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .chat .bubble {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
      border-radius: 4px 12px 12px 12px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }
    .chat .bubble-meta {
      font: 12px/1.4 ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .chat .bubble pre {
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      font: 12px/1.55 ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      font: 600 11px/1.4 ui-monospace, monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--pink);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .lede {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #334155;
      margin: 8px 0 28px;
      max-width: 56ch;
    }
    .lede em { color: var(--dim); font-style: italic; }
    .cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }
    .cta .key { color: var(--text); }
    .cta .plus { color: var(--dim); }
    .hint { margin-top: 12px; color: var(--dim); font-size: 13px; }

    ol.steps {
      list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;
      display: grid; gap: 4px;
      counter-reset: step;
    }
    ol.steps li {
      counter-increment: step;
      padding: 14px 16px 14px 56px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      position: relative;
    }
    ol.steps li::before {
      content: counter(step);
      position: absolute;
      left: 16px; top: 14px;
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(78, 27, 145, 0.10);
      color: var(--accent);
      font: 600 13px/28px ui-monospace, monospace;
      text-align: center;
    }
    ol.steps li h3 { margin: 0 0 2px; }
    ol.steps li p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }

    .cards {
      display: grid; gap: 12px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
    }
    .card h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 15px; }
    .card p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</Base>
